# Design System

**Calm, Contemplative, Clarity.** The design should feel like a well-crafted journal.

## Colours

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| Background | `#FAF9F7` (warm cream) | Page background; never pure white |
| Card/elevated | `#FFFFFF` | Cards, panels |
| Hover/subtle | `#F5F3F0` | Hover states, selected items |
| Text primary | `#2C2C2C` (soft black) | Body text; never pure black |
| Text secondary | `#6B6B6B` | Supporting text |
| Text tertiary | `#9A9A9A` | Disabled, meta labels |
| Border primary | `#E8E6E3` | Barely visible borders |
| Border subtle | `#F0EEEB` | Inner separators |
| Accent | `#7A6B5A` (warm taupe) | Interactive elements, focus rings |
| Drag handle | `#C4BDB4` | Bottom sheet handle |

## Typography

- **Headings**: `font-heading` (serif, e.g. Newsreader)
- **Body/UI**: System sans-serif (default Tailwind stack)
- Page heading: `text-2xl font-heading font-normal leading-[1.3]`
- Section heading: `text-lg font-heading font-normal leading-[1.4]`
- Body: `text-sm leading-relaxed`
- Labels: `text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider`

## Visual Rules

1. **NO border-radius** on cards, buttons, or inputs (square corners only)
2. **NO shadows** except `shadow-[0_-4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]` on bottom sheet
3. **NO gradients** in UI elements
4. **Transitions**: Always `duration-300 ease-out`

## Component Patterns

```tsx
// Buttons — secondary (default)
className="border border-[#E8E6E3] bg-transparent text-[#2C2C2C]
           hover:bg-[#F5F3F0] hover:border-[#E8E6E3]
           transition duration-300 ease-out"

// Links — accent
className="text-[#7A6B5A] underline underline-offset-2
           hover:text-[#5A4B3A]"

// Focus rings
className="focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2
           focus-visible:ring-[#7A6B5A]
           focus-visible:ring-offset-2
           focus-visible:ring-offset-[#FAF9F7]"
```

## Accessibility

- All interactive elements must have visible focus states
- Semantic HTML structure (`nav`, `region`, `heading` levels)
- Minimum 4.5:1 contrast for text
- Keyboard navigable; `aria-label` on icon-only buttons
